        <td style="width:328px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Model-View-Presenter</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> (MVP) is the graphical user interface (GUI) framework used by Dolphin Smalltalk. It a modern equivalent of the original MVC framework found in Smalltalk-80.</text></para>
        </td>
