    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The term, </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Model View Presenter</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, was first used by the user interface framework of the same name, designed by Taligent Systems for the C++ language. Dolphin&apos;s MVP is loosely based on this work.</text><snippet src="Tip_Of_The_Day_Footer"/></para>
